        <div type="bibliography">
           <p>The inscription was first edited by Holle (<bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:Holle1877_02"></ptr><citedRange>586-587</citedRange></bibl>, in Javanese script); it was edited again by Saleh Danasasmita (<bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:Saleh Danasasmita1975_01"></ptr></bibl>) and by Hasan Djafar (<bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:HasanDjafar1991_01"></ptr><citedRange>16-18</citedRange></bibl>). Although these scholars have discussed the meaning if the chronogram, only Saleh Danasasmita furnished a full translation and interpretation. Re-edited and translated here by Aditia Gunawan &amp; Arlo Griffiths, based on the OD photo.</p>
